article_id:751,category_name:News,title_name:First Anniversary Events Are Live![Update],image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/262a015b96330a2bd037e7865c5db5c0.png,message:<div>Events for the first anniversary started <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/262a015b96330a2bd037e7865c5db5c0.png"></div><hr><div><strong><u>1. Daily Free Tenfold Summons Are Here! Summon Up to 100 Times During the Event!</u></strong></div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcases for free once per day, started <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>!</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/759">See here for more information.</a></div><hr><div><strong><u>2. A Platinum Showcase Is Now Live! 5★ Gala Dragalia Adventurer Guaranteed!</u></strong></div><div>A Platinum Showcase where one of the 5★ Gala Dragalia adventurers is guaranteed to appear in the tenfold summon is now live!</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/750">See here for more information.</a></div><hr><div><strong><u>3. Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!</u></strong></div><div>A Gala Dragalia featuring Gala Dragalia adventurers is now live!</div><div><br></div><div>■Gala Dragalia Event Duration</div><div>・Gala Prince featured period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569995940"></span></div><div><br></div><div>・Gala Cleo, Gala Mym, Gala Ranzal, and Gala Sarisse featured period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569996000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570168740"></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(209, 72, 65);">Note: The initial 5★ and 5★ featured appearance rate is different than the one from before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569995940"></span>. Additionally, increases to the 5★ and 5★ featured appearance rate before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569995940"></span> will not be carried over, and will return to the initial 6% when the featured adventurers change.</span></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/jp/news/detail/748">See here for more information.</a></div><hr><div><strong><u>4. First Anniversary Limited-Time Packs Are Here!</u></strong></div><div>First Anniversary packs are available for a limited time under Value Packs in the Shop as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>!</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/jp/news/detail/754">See here for more information.</a></div><hr><div><strong><u>5. First Anniversary Bonus!</u></strong></div><div>Get the following incredible rewards when you log in during the event duration!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f9dfab250f25b6fdeeeedd8822d508af.png"></div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1572674399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・The log-in bonus will be sent to you every day after 6:00 AM when you log in.</div><div>・Gifts sent as log-in bonuses can only be accepted for a limited time.</div><hr><div><strong><u>6. Extra Skip Tickets!</u></strong></div><div>For a limited time, we will increase the number of skip tickets obtained each day as log-in bonuses to 10.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/46cc89c8e834a3cb572d9c9cdd89ca6e.png"></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1571378399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・The log-in bonus skip tickets will be added directly every day after 6:00 AM when you log in.</div><div>・If the number of skip tickets you possess exceeds the maximum of 200, the excess will be lost.</div><hr><div><strong><u>7. Events and Endeavors Useful for Upgrading Your Team and Facilities!</u></strong></div><div><br></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(209, 213, 216);"><strong>The Imperial Onslaught Double Drops Event:</strong></span></div><div>During the event, drop rewards you can obtain from The Imperial Onslaught will be doubled!</div><div>Note: This does not apply to wyrmprints or astral pieces.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569823199"></span></div><div><br></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(209, 213, 216);"><strong>Avenue to Power and Dragon Trials Double Drops Event:</strong></span></div><div>During the event, drop rewards you can obtain from Avenue to Power and Dragon Trials will be doubled!</div><div>Note: This does not apply to wyrmprints or astral pieces.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569995999"></span></div><div><br></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(209, 213, 216);"><strong>First Anniversary Entry-Level Endeavors:</strong></span></div><div>During the event, there will be limited-time endeavors with exciting rewards.</div><div>For more information about these endeavors, check Endeavors on the home page.</div><div><span style="color: rgb(44, 130, 201);"><strong>Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569586200"></span>]<br></strong></span>For players unable to complete the endeavors requiring you to unlock mana circles for lack of mana circles left to unlock, please wait until the start of the upcoming raid event.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570427999"></span></div><div><br></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(209, 213, 216);"><strong>Main Campaign Half-Stamina Event:</strong></span></div><div>During the event, stamina expended while playing the main campaign will be cut in half.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1572501599"></span></div><div><br></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(209, 213, 216);"><strong>Avenue to Fortune and Elemental Ruins Double Drops Event:</strong></span></div><div>During the event, the amount of rupies earned from Avenue to Fortune and drop rewards obtained from Elemental Ruins will be doubled!</div><div>Also, the Expert difficulty will be open for all Elemental Ruins quests for the duration of this event.</div><div>Note: This does not apply to weapons, wyrmprints, or astral pieces.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569996000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570427999"></span></div><hr><div><strong><u>8. Six Free Item Summons Event Is Now Live!</u></strong></div><div>A Six Free Item Summons Event, where you can perform six item summons per day for free, started <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1571378340"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・You can summon items for free six times per day (each day is from 6:00 AM to 5:59 AM the next day).</div><div>・The six free item summons reset each day at 6:00 AM.</div><div>・It is not possible to obtain adventurers, weapons, wyrmprints, or dragons via item summons.</div><hr><div><strong><u>9. Special First Anniversary Voice Lines!</u></strong></div><div>Special voiced lines have been added to adventurers for a limited time starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Playing the Voiced Lines</div><div>On the Adventurers screen or the Edit Team screen, tap or press and hold the adventurer whose voice you wish to hear, then tap the magnifying glass icon in the bottom right corner of the screen. Tapping the &quot;1st&quot; icon will play the special first anniversary voice line.</div><div><br></div><div>■Availability</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1571378399"></span></div><hr><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1569564000,update_time1569586090